1. You can declare a DTD externally and then associate it with more than one XML document.
Ans: True

2. Declare an element named TEST that can contain other elements or text.
Ans: <!ELEMENT TEST ANY>

3. With attribute types, which of the following can be used to indicate any literal string?
Ans: CDATA

4. With element declaration, select the option that indicates that the releaseDate is optional.
Ans: releaseDate?
